      </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nives-celsius-3.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4163","checkdouble":"191046"},{"date":"15:09 12/07","title":"10 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 khi Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn CLB Juventus l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111ang ch\u1edd ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ph\u00e1 khi \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n t\u1edbi Turin.</h2><h2>1. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn b\u1ed9 3 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Anh, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Italia</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean b\u1ee5c vinh quang nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Premier League, La Liga v\u00e0 Serie A.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu c\u00f9ng Juve gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam Scudetto trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi m\u00e0 'B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0' \u0111ang n\u1eafm k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 7 l\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2011/12 t\u1edbi nay.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus lan thu 6 lien tiep doat Scudetto\" title=\"Juventus l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111o\u1ea1t Scudetto\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/5/22/juventus-30-crotone-thien-duong-thu-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sang Juventus, Ronaldo&nbsp;s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u1edbi 3 CLB kh\u00e1c nhau</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u1edbi 3 CLB kh\u00e1c nhau trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i AC Milan, Clarence Seedorf. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Ajax, Real Madrid v\u00e0 AC Milan.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu CR7 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f9ng Juve, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 anh s\u1ebd b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Seedorf m\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u00f9ng 3 CLB kh\u00e1c nhau l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t (6 l\u1ea7n) so v\u1edbi 4 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Seedorf.</p>\r\n<h2>3. V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 6 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, CR7 s\u1ebd s\u00e1nh ngang v\u1edbi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Real Paco Gento - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia 6 danh hi\u1ec7u C1 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1956 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 1965. Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ean th\u00ec Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111ang 'v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i' v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap s\u1edf h\u1eefu.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo huong loi neu toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i n\u1ebfu t\u1edbi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/emre-can-hao-huc-truoc-co-hoi-choi-bong-cung-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ronaldo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 1 danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League n\u1ebfu t\u1edbi Juventus</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u QBV nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roanldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111ang c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh 5 QBV th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean CR7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1edfi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 2017/18 c\u00f9ng m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 'ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m' trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh&nbsp;danh hi\u1ec7u QBV th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</p>\r\n<h2>5. Gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh sau nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i M.U (m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2007/08) v\u00e0 Real Madrid (c\u00e1c m\u00f9a 2010/11, 2013/14 v\u00e0 2014/15). Chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh b\u1edbt kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Serie A, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 CR7 gi\u00e0nh Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 5 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>6. Ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i Serie A</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Higuain v\u1edbi 36 b\u00e0n trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Napoli. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo t\u1eebng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c n\u00e0y \u1edf c\u00e1c m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i (2010-11, 2011-12, 2014-15).</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo la cau thu dat gia nhat lich su Juventus.\" title=\"Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Juventus.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ronaldo \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i Serie A cho Juventus.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>7. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Serie A</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n cho Juventus l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ferenc Herzer v\u1edbi 35 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 1925/26. N\u1ebfu Ronaldo ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n 100 n\u0103m n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>8. Ghi nhi\u1ec1u hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Champions League</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 7 c\u00fa hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 khi l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Juve, Ronaldo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1eadp th\u00eam nh\u1eefng hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1.</p>\r\n<h2>9. V\u01b0\u1ee3t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u1eadp hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Serie A</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u1eadp hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Serie A l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 Gunnar Nordahl v\u00e0 Giuseppe Meazza \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 17 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 n\u1ebfu anh c\u1ee9 ghi trung b\u00ecnh 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 c\u00fa hat-trick trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<h2>10. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi khi ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i M.U c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf Real Madrid. V\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u1ebfu ghi b\u00e0n s\u00f2n s\u00f2n \u1edf Juve.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 John Charles v\u00e0 Christian Vieri \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y v\u1edbi hai gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo-180-190973.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo-180-190973.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm thay Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/infographics/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi-406-190961.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/infographics/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi-406-190961.html\">Infographics: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid - Ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e2u, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-khong-the-xay-ra-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec b\u1ecb M.U ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c, Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111i theo &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; Juventus</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, th\u00f4ng tin Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CR7 m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Man...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4162","checkdouble":"191027"},{"date":"15:32 12/07","title":"Juve s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p CR7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/world-cup-2018-vang-nhung-cu-vo-le-nga-ban-den-doc-dao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Juve l\u00e0 CLB cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, sau khi si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2>CR7 gia nh\u1eadp Serie A<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">112 tri\u1ec7u euro l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfn Juventus ph\u1ea3i chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo &ndash; si\u00eau sao \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, v\u00e0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. 9 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Los Blancos, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Serie A v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng \u1edf Real Madrid, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng bi\u1ebft \u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u00ec t\u00ecnh y\u00eau m\u00e0 t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00e3y hi\u1ec3u cho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; CR7 cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juve l\u00e0 CLB cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo\" title=\"Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/world-cup-2018-vang-nhung-cu-vo-le-nga-ban-den-doc-dao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juve l\u00e0 CLB cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jorge Mendes c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng cho anh \u1ea5y. Juve l\u00e0 CLB cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Andrea Agnelli, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo, v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o c\u00f9ng Real Madrid. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u01a1n G\u0110\u0110H Beppe Marotta v\u00ec s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y&rdquo; &ndash; si\u00eau c\u00f2 Jorge Mendes cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cris Ronaldo \u0111ang \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf Hy L\u1ea1p sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft CLB Juventus v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai tu\u1ea7n sau. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Real Madrid, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea1o chi trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8, \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\">10 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 khi Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn CLB Juventus l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111ang ch\u1edd ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu-172-191022.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu-172-191022.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: &ldquo;K\u1ebb hai m\u1eb7t&rdquo; Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</span><br>\r\nThay v\u00ec tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United, Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Jose Mourinho d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4161","checkdouble":"191028"},{"date":"15:22 12/07","title":"VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam song cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0110T U23 \u00dac \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda VFF.</h2><h2>VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1edbi 8 t\u1edbi, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng ra t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng quy t\u1ee5 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m 'thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao' cho \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/giai-quoc-te-u-23-3_emlc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan, U23 Oman v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng U23 \u00dac. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do L\u0110B\u0110 \u00dac kh\u00f4ng thu x\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y n\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U19 tham d\u1ef1. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, BTC gi\u1ea3i \u0111ang t\u00ednh t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed9i Australia b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 t\u1eebng l\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4160","checkdouble":"191038"},{"date":"16:30 12/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/6/hlv-park-hang-seo-co-nguy-co-mat-tro-cung-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea7m c\u01a1 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c n\u00e0y, trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u V-League \u0111\u1ec3 quan s\u00e1t c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-co-nguy-co-mat-tro-cung-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 su\u1ea5t cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean lo l\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 'th\u00e9p' Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 6. T\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t 3 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997, khi m\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n trong 10 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 23/7 t\u1edbi, ngay sau khi v\u00f2ng 20 V-League k\u1ebft th\u00fac. \u0110\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 7/8 tr\u00ean SV\u0110 QG M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u1edbi 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung-168-191038.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung-168-191038.html\">VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam song cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0110T U23 \u00dac \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda VFF.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/dtqg/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018-292-190436.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/dtqg/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018-292-190436.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 khi c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4159","checkdouble":"191049"}]}